                "institute": "3INDNSD"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The 7-Be beam of energy 20.25 MeV was",
                "separated at 0 degree using the recoil mass",
                "spectrometer HIRA (Heavy Ion Reaction Analyzer)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
